column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,  p.deVRad_u,p.deVRadErr_u,p.deVRad_z,p.deVRadErr_z, g.lgm_tot_p5#,  p.z, s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift, s.mjd FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN galSpecExtra AS g ON g.specobjid = s.specobjid WHERE  s.class = &&&  AND g.lgm_tot_p5# > #  AND s.z BETWEEN # AND #
